0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"樓主個名咁串嘅"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"屌 樓主原來引伏 一條都無答 backlist佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:22:37.000Z","msg":"Sor呀啱啱做緊嘢 冇覆 唔好blacklist我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1573afe71dc88383d6f74b96af8585c155fe5b73","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10308bfa5b0b0214562a73859d652c43ff994a12","tid":2154480,"uid":212878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"多唔多野讀 讀完諗住做咩機構 聽講飽和難揾社工做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"Ummm 我就覺得唔算多 都係讀下theory，仲有啲core course 係比你認識一下自己，可以了解多啲自己咩性格，對於你將來做唔做社工好有幫助<br />\n<br />\n以前做過b仔記pt 有啲想入返去<br />\n唔會考慮細/獨立機構 對社工冇咩保障<br />\n<br />\n只要你肯做eld rehab個啲 流動性其實都好高 算係好多fg容易搵到工嘅機構"},{"pid":"e2759c235aca2f5b0f22b2620fddd1888d4f7a03","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edfc491cf1b7844d22090aceb0bebd4725ba2357","tid":2154480,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"廚房幾大?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffba10f683a0f4c396dcd30d70318e6f5c5e58fb","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5b42f90fa85a28267b7477dbde81d3c5575e3ad","tid":2154480,"uid":231234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:32:47.000Z","msg":"點解想做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"覺得自己好廢 讀書個陣冇咩目標 冇咩想做 計數又唔叻 英文又講得唔夠人好<br />\n結果自己個分夠入sw<br />\n同埋以前同學校社工好frd<br />\n所以就諗起社工呢個出路<br />\n讀完都會想入返呢行"},{"pid":"16ca15c0532c6508c343d7466fd99610c5410bb0","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"自推...<br />\n真係柒咗 出完po真係有嘢做覆唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd789ad3418e78930cc72460d0a5814869d50f","tid":2154480,"uid":97766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"社工同Counsellor主要有咩大分別 / 社工多唔多counselling嘅野做？"},{"pid":"75f52a0e15c37697d8d7d75e233299a6213deb79","tid":2154480,"uid":349476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8fcd789ad3418e78930cc72460d0a5814869d50f","tid":2154480,"uid":97766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"社工同Counsellor主要有咩大分別 / 社工多唔多counselling嘅野做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:08:12.000Z","msg":"路過答<br />\nCounsellor 主要用案主自身資源去幫佢<br />\n社工除咗會運用自身資源，同時都會用社會資源去幫案主<br />\n<br />\n以輔助就業社工為例，如果社工淨係同佢係間房做輔導，靠佢自己去改善工作表現/面試技巧/提供工作動力，咁個幫助會比較弱，同時都睇唔到現實案主面對既情況。<br />\n所以輔助就業都會有同相熟既僱主有linkage，可能係有心公司/社企等等，運用更多社會資源去協助案主。<br />\n<br />\n多唔多counselling 既野就睇下你搵邊類工，例如精神復康/成癮服務就比較重輔導，都係睇你個職位工作內容，同埋workload 會唔會太重。社工唔只係得一個方法去幫人，輔導只係一部分，都要同時兼顧其他工作，例如小組/大型活動/協調前線同事/同其他專業合作/申請社會資源等等"},{"pid":"698718e67ecfdf716e1e7ac62b11002f8794db57","tid":2154480,"uid":349476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbe9c1c2dac7b3365125b8c7f69870581099e266","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85646dfdaa3eb32d80ebd6d810e05a21a2be6812","tid":2154480,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"點睇途人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"咩途人呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"佢係咪講緊YouTuber肥EE個朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8a2a63eccb6f18a6b1554ce888bd7f1ce92f02","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fcd789ad3418e78930cc72460d0a5814869d50f","tid":2154480,"uid":97766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"社工同Counsellor主要有咩大分別 / 社工多唔多counselling嘅野做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"會覺得社工會接觸埋counsellor嘅工作，但未必好深入，而且社工好多角度，例如會幫助你client去獲取社區資源，申請援助個啲。<br />\n而counsellor就係好專業深入去做不同種類嘅輔導，社工未必可以做到咁足。<br />\n<br />\n而多唔多counselling嘢做就好彩你做邊個field，例如做多case work嘅field eg outreach個啲可能需要多啲"},{"pid":"70724372d9f1fbe493620482bd4370e3349b6c52","tid":2154480,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19f84526a619ac3e9d95ca7fadb790267b0a194f","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"😹勿相認<br />\n都係無聊所以玩下你問我答<br />\n歡迎問 唔知有冇人覆機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e6c4c7a67604f1a3760d398ab94d34ed1da18a","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70724372d9f1fbe493620482bd4370e3349b6c52","tid":2154480,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19f84526a619ac3e9d95ca7fadb790267b0a194f","tid":2154480,"uid":355363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:03:44.000Z","msg":"😹勿相認<br />\n都係無聊所以玩下你問我答<br />\n歡迎問 唔知有冇人覆機呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T17:53:54.000Z","msg":"社工呢行搵工interview會睇性格多過你成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊到出身唔緊要 最緊要你有做社工嘅氣質或者堅持<br />\n比老細睇到你團火<br />\n佢自然會請你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}